mb.append("<font face=arial size=+1 color=#666666>");


mb.append("Want to announce your web log to your friends without making a pesky phone call?  Easy.  Enter their email address and they’ll be invited.  Then enjoy checking the status of your invitations - Open, Viewed, Accepted, Rejected.  Add a list of friends in your profile and then network away.  Send them a note from your log or from their log.  They can send you a note from their log or your log.  Send a note to all of your friends at once.  Weve the web.  Give rise to a cozy little family of bloggers.  You can even see a list of recent posts made by your friends.  Stay in the loop.");
